stickerText: The doctor that injects you makes a HUGE difference.
I had tried a neurologist in both Oregon and Texas and neither helped.
THEN I found an award winning neurologist in San Diego and she CHANGED MY LIFE.
Research neurologists in your area that are covered by your insurance and find a migraine/botox SPECIALIST.

7184546006128807214.desc: Watch the whole thing before you judge 🤗 What questions do you have about my journey? #celiacdisease #chronicmigraine #chronicillness #chronicpain #celiac #autoimmunedisease #botox #botoxinjection #botoxstory #medicalbotox

stickerText: I GET BOTOX EVERY 3 MONTHS AT 22 YEARS OLD

Philz order reveal
at the end 🤪
*15 DAYS of migraine a month. Some migraines last multiple days.
I’VE TRIED OVER 15 MEDICATIONS and even more supplements and other “cures”. If you’ve heard of it I’ve tried it.
A combo of a daily preventative, medical Botox, a gluten free diet, and an ab0rt1ve (take at onset of symptoms) have CHANGED MY LIFE. I’m so thankful I can live normally again.

7178638984514555182.desc: IT CANT JUST BE ME. Raise your hand in the chat if… 🙋🏼‍♀️ As someone with an autoimmune disorder, chronic migraine, & hypermobility/maybe hEDS (lots of injuries and surgeries) I’ve spent YEARS frustrated with the medical industry trying to get answers. I’m thankful I have good insurance & the answers now but it was a long journey to get here. If you don’t have answers yet KEEP FIGHTING AND STANDING UP FOR YOURSELF! I believe in you 🫶🏼🤍😊 #chronicillness #chronicillnessawareness #chronicillnesswarrior #chronicwellness #chronicpain #chronicmigraine #celiacdisease #celiac #hypermobility #hybermobilecheck #chronicillnessstruggles #chronicillnesssupport
7178638984514555182.author: maliaglutenfree

stickerText: Chronic illness gang I HAVE A QUESTION FOR YOU
“How many you have ever felt personally victimized by…?!”
Test after test leading to no conclusions
“There’s nothing you can do, we’ve tried everything”
Years without knowing what’s wrong with you
Prescribed countless medications with terrible side effects
Prescribing medications over a holistic wellness approach
You are strong for dealing with chronic illness AND the endless barriers we have to jump. KEEP FIGHTING 🤍
